title: UFYB 113: Listener Q&A: Goals, New Year Resolutions, Dating, Love & Sex
itunes:title: Listener Q&A: Goals, New Year Resolutions, Dating, Love & Sex
description:
I hope my answers are helpful in getting you into the new year with a well-managed mind to create all the results you want. I’m sharing my thoughts on unrequited love and whether it’s a problem, the basis of libido and sexual attraction, and how to ask better questions when it comes to creating anything that you want in your life.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://unfuckyourbrain.com/113
